log.content: I would like you to create an svg image of a sunset through the mountains. Make sure the result is visible in index.html

function.name: create_file
function.arguments:
{"filename":"sunset_mountains.svg","content":"<svg width="500" height="300">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="skyGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#87CEEB" />
      <stop offset="65%" stop-color="#4682B4" />
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  <rect width="500" height="300" fill="url(#skyGradient)"/>
  <!-- Mountains -->
  <polygon points="150,250 250,180 350,250" style="fill:#48D1CC;stroke-width:1;stroke:#000"/>
  <polygon points="250,70 350,150 450,70" style="fill:#BADA55;stroke-width:1;stroke:#000"/>
</svg>"}
